Step 1 — Create the slot
az webapp deployment slot create --resource-group emeka-rg --name emeka-website-txgekkysrjei4 --slot staging
This creates a separate slot at:
https://emeka-website-txgekkysrjei4-staging.azurewebsites.net
Step 2 — Deploy your files to the staging slot
az webapp deploy --resource-group emeka-rg --name emeka-website-txgekkysrjei4 --slot staging --src-path site.zip --type zip
Step 3 — Preview & test it
https://emeka-website-txgekkysrjei4-staging.azurewebsites.net
Step 4 — Swap staging into production (when ready)
az webapp deployment slot swap --resource-group emeka-rg --name emeka-website-txgekkysrjei4 --slot staging --target-slot production
How it all fits together
production slot  →  https://emeka-website-txgekkysrjei4.azurewebsites.net  (live)
